#
Alias      MyK*0       K*0
Alias      Myanti-K*0  anti-K*0
ChargeConj MyK*0       Myanti-K*0  
#
Decay B_s0sig
  1.000    MyK*0   Myanti-K*0   SVV_HELAMP Aplus pAplus Azero pAzero Aminus pAminus;
Enddecay
CDecay anti-B_s0sig
#
